      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; single pump specimen used for validation testing.",
      "rationale": "Validation testing was performed on a single pump specimen manufactured to nominal dimensions. Sample-to-sample variability assessment is not required at MRL 2. Dimensional inspection confirmed the test article was within ±0.05 mm of nominal geometry."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
