      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; qualitative assessment of parameter equivalency between validation and COU conditions documented.",
      "rationale": "A qualitative mapping between validation experiment conditions and COU conditions was performed. The primary difference is the use of bovine blood versus human blood in clinical use; this is addressed under the Relevance of Validation Activities factor. Formal equivalency quantification is not required at MRL 2."
