    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out as not required at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device hemolysis tolerance decision. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 was confirmed for all geometric variants at the identified worst-case operating condition (4 L/min, 2400 RPM). The credibility package is accepted for submission.",
